# Source material is DVC-tracked, not committed. Nothing sensitive in git.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!books/
!videos/
!books/raw/.gitkeep
!books/processed/.gitkeep
!videos/raw/.gitkeep
!videos/processed/.gitkeep
books/raw/*
books/processed/*
videos/raw/*
videos/processed/*
!books/README.md
!videos/README.md
